@push_leverage_positions
title: Push for more positions
view-if: parlament_coalition_leverage < 10
choose-if: parlament_coalition_push < psc_tripartite_coalition_phase and psc_tripartite_coalition_phase < 3
unavailable-subtitle: We've already pushed for more. [? if psc_tripartite_coalition_phase < 3: We'll have to wait for the next round of negotiations to try again. ?]
on-arrival: {!
    if (Q.psc_tripartite_coalition_phase == 1) {
        Q.psc_relations -= 5;
        Q[Q.parlament_current_icv + "_relations"] -= 3;
    } else {
        Q.psc_relations -= 3;
        Q[Q.parlament_current_icv + "_relations"] -= 2;
    }
    Q.parlament_coalition_leverage += 4;
    Q.parlament_coalition_push += 1;
!}
go-to: changes

@send_back
title: Send this counter-proposal
view-if: parlament_coalition_changes
subtitle: [? if parlament_coalition_push >= psc_tripartite_coalition_phase: Back-and-forth will take time but may give us a better position. ?]
on-arrival: {!
    Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = true;
    if (Q.parlament_coalition_push >= Q.psc_tripartite_coalition_phase) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = false;
    } else {
        Q.psc_relations -= 2;
        if (Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_vp == "erc" && Q.erc_parlament_s <= Q.parlament_current_icv_s && Q.psc_tripartite_coalition_phase != 3) {
            Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = false;
        }
        if (Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_economy == "erc" && Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_interior == "erc" && Q.psc_tripartite_coalition_phase < 2) {
            Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = false;
        }
    }
!}
go-to: decision

@decision
title: decision
go-to: accept if parlament_coalition_proposal_accept; next_phase if parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = false

@next_phase
title: next phase
go-to: new_elections if psc_tripartite_coalition_phase >= 3; new_phase_2 if not psc_tripartite_coalition_phase >= 3

@new_phase_2
on-arrival: {!
    Q.parlament_coalition_changes = false;
    Q.psc_tripartite_coalition_phase += 1;
    Q.month_actions += 1;
    Q.independence_trust -= 2;
    Q.social_dissent += 3;
!}

The PSC's and [+ parlament_current_icv +]'s representatives were not fully satisfied with our counter-proposal. [? if parlament_coalition_proposal_vp = "erc" and erc_parlament_s <= parlament_current_icv_s:  Demanding the Vice-Presidency when [+ parlament_current_icv +] is the larger partner raised eyebrows. ?][? if parlament_coalition_proposal_economy = "erc" and parlament_coalition_proposal_interior = "erc": Demanding both Economy and Interior at once was seen as overreaching. ?]We'll have to wait for the next round of negotiations.

- @post_event: And so, time passes...


@accept
title: Accept proposal
choose-if: not parlament_coalition_changes
unavailable-subtitle: We have proposed changes which will require PSC and [+ parlament_current_icv +] approval.
on-arrival: {!
    Q.psc_tripartite_coalition_phase = 0;
    Q.cat_coalition_disp = "<span style='color: var(--psc); font-style: italic;'>New Tripartite</span> Government";
    Q.erc_in_gob = true;
    Q.erc_supporting = true;
    Q.cup_in_gob = false;
    Q.cup_supporting = false;
    Q.cat_coalition = ["psc", "erc", Q.parlament_current_icv];
    Q.cat_coalition_dissent = 0;
    Q.position_disp = "Generalitat";
    Q.independence_trust -= 5;
!}

After rounds of negotiations, we've agreed to join PSC and [+ parlament_current_icv +] in a [+ cat_coalition_disp +].

- @parlament_coalition_resolve: A new government is formed


@new_elections
title: new elections
on-arrival: {!
    Q.psc_tripartite_coalition_phase = 0;
    Q.psc_relations -= 5;
    Q[Q.parlament_current_icv + "_relations"] -= 3;
    Q.social_dissent += 5;
    Q.snap_blame = Q.player_party;
    Q.snap_counterparty = "psc";
    Q.snap_severity = 0.12;
!}
call: snap_election

After three rounds of negotiations, we were unable to agree on a fair distribution of government positions with the PSC and [+ parlament_current_icv +]. New elections will have to decide the matter.

- @post_event: We'll have to see if we fare any better this time...
